Kore 3.0 adds many exciting new features.

We'll go over the major features here, But there will be some small changes you might notice in the shortcut.

Firstly, All of the menus have had a complete redesign. This is huge news. everything looks so much cleaner and way more elegant.
We have added a lot of new shortcuts.
You can now have custom a USER ID.
When changing versions, you won't have to input your name everytime (this is thanks to a new internal structure).
New Koremands.
Koremand prompt is now located in settings to make everything seem less crowded.
Better update screen for out of date clients.
New menu for when youre not connected to the internet.
New Welcome screen for first time users.
The ability to reset Kore in settings.
A few minor bug fixes.
